30
00:02:14,840 --> 00:02:17,840
TONIGHT, A STAR FELL FROM THE SKY
今夜，一顆流星從天而降

31
00:02:29,240 --> 00:02:31,440
I MADE A WISH
我許了一個願

32
00:02:50,720 --> 00:02:54,760
I WISHED THAT THEY ALL DIE
