Why?
為什麼？

58
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:33,160
What happened?
發生了什麼？

59
00:06:33,640 --> 00:06:36,520
You had alcohol poisoning when you arrived.
你酒精中毒了

60
00:06:49,160 --> 00:06:50,360
Nevra?
內芙拉？

61
