- Someone sent you flowers, Zuhal. - Who?
-有人給你送花了，祖哈爾-誰？

100
00:10:33,680 --> 00:10:37,240
- Me. - You can leave when you're feeling better.
-我  -感覺好一些了就可以出院

101
