- You didn't go? - No.
-你冇走嗎？-冇

102
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:43,360
You were here through the night?
你整夜都在這裏嗎？

103
00:11:04,760 --> 00:11:05,760
Hello?
餵？

104
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:08,160
Yes, I'm here.
對，我在這

105
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,320
I have the file.
文件在我這

106
00:11:10,520 --> 00:11:11,880
Where are you?
你在哪？

107
00:11:12,960 --> 00:11:13,960
Hello?
餵？

108
00:11:14,560 --> 00:11:17,400
Hello? You're breaking up. Hello?
餵？信號不好  餵？

109
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:21,440
Cemil, I'm so sorry.
塞米爾，我很抱歉

110
00:11:22,200 --> 00:11:26,680
I'm so embarrassed. I don't know what to say.
我好尷尬  不知道該說些什麼

111
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:32,800
I can't even imagine the spot I put you in.
我甚至無法想象我把你放在了什麼位置

112
00:11:34,800 --> 00:11:36,680
I should quit the job.
我應該辭職

113
00:11:39,640 --> 00:11:41,840
What am I to do, Cemil?
我該怎麼辦，塞米爾？

114
00:11:44,880 --> 00:11:46,920
WATER IT TWICE A WEEK
每周澆水兩次

115
00:11:47,000 --> 00:11:49,240
Water it twice a week...
每周澆水兩次

116
00:11:50,440 --> 00:11:53,840
And come with me. Let's go.
跟我一起走吧

117
00:12:03,480 --> 00:12:06,960
- What will you do now? - Get back to Istanbul.
-你現在要做什麼？-回到伊斯坦佈爾

118
00:12:09,200 --> 00:12:10,520
I need to ask you something.
我要問你一件事

119
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:13,840
Why did you lie, Selim and you?
你為什麼撒謊，塞利姆和你？

120
00:12:13,920 --> 00:12:15,760
About how the house burned down.
關於房子如何被燒毀的

121
00:12:16,560 --> 00:12:18,160
Why would I lie?
我為什麼要撒謊？

122
00:12:19,680 --> 00:12:20,560
I already told you.
我已經跟你說過

123
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:24,200
Selim forgets to take his pills and hallucinates.
塞利姆忘了吃藥 産生了幻想

124
00:12:25,640 --> 00:12:28,800
- That's all. - Fine. If you say so.
-就是這樣  -好吧，如果你這樣說的話

125
00:12:30,400 --> 00:12:32,680
Why wouldn't I tell you if I knew something?
如果我知道什麼，我為什麼不告訴你？

126
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:36,040
There's something that scares you. I'd forgotten about it.
有一些會讓你害怕的事情我都已經忘記了

127
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,600
What's that?
什麼事？

128
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:41,200
You're scared of being left alone. You always were.
你總是害怕一個人呆著

129
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:44,720
What would you do if something were to happen to Selim?
如果塞利姆發生什麼事情，你會怎麼做？

130
00:12:45,280 --> 00:12:48,080
If you knew that I was scared of being left alone,
如果你知道我害怕一個人呆著，

131
00:12:48,160 --> 00:12:49,720
why did you up and leave?
那你為什麼離開？

132
00:12:50,720 --> 00:12:53,200
You didn't take me to Istanbul.
你冇帶我去伊斯坦佈爾

133
00:12:53,280 --> 00:12:56,400
You were being scared of loneliness, and I was scared of you.
你怕寂寞，而我怕你

134
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:59,720
Fine! Then don't come here with tears in your eyes ever again.
好！那就別再流眼淚了

135
00:13:01,040 --> 00:13:04,360
Why shouldn't I? Didn't you tell me not to be afraid of being afraid?
為什麼不呢？你不是告訴我不要害怕嗎？

136
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:05,520
Take care.
照顧好自己

137
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,120
Hello?
餵？

138
00:13:22,280 --> 00:13:24,480
You're breaking up. I can't hear you.
信號不好，我聽不到你說話

139
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,520
Hello?
餵？

140
00:13:29,440 --> 00:13:30,440
Hello?
餵？

141
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,480
The door is opening.
門開了

142
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:46,000
Stop! Stop!
站住！別動！

143
00:13:46,840 --> 00:13:49,240
Call the police! Call the police, Galip!
報警！加利普！報警！

144
00:13:49,800 --> 00:13:51,440
- Are you alright? - Take your gun.
-你還好嗎？-拿槍

145
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:53,520
Are you alright?
你還好嗎？

146
00:13:56,640 --> 00:13:59,120
- What happened? Did they find him? - I just got word.
-發生了什麼？他們找到他了嗎？-我剛得到消息

147
00:13:59,200 --> 00:14:01,440
He's trapped in a shopping centre's garage.
他被睏在購物中心的車庫裏

148
00:14:19,880 --> 00:14:21,880
Yes. We have all the exits blocked.
是的，我們已將所有出口都被封鎖了

149
00:14:21,960 --> 00:14:23,800
This is the only exit. He's definitely in here.
這是唯一的出口  他肯定在這裏

150
00:14:25,000 --> 00:14:26,000
Let's go!
我們走吧！

151
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,640
I found his costume. He's going up to the roof!
我發現了他的服裝  他上屋頂了！

152
00:15:35,040 --> 00:15:36,040
To be honest...
老實說

153
00:15:37,800 --> 00:15:40,280
I don't even like the taste of alcohol, Cemil.
我甚至不喜歡酒精的味道，塞米爾

154
00:15:41,720 --> 00:15:45,560
But after I have that first glass...
但是當我喝了第一杯之後

155
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:49,160
Something happens...
有些事情發生了

156
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,880
I can't stop myself.
我無法阻止自己

157
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:58,040
All I want to do is drink.
我隻想喝酒

158
00:15:58,120 --> 00:16:00,560
No matter what.
無論如何都要喝

159
00:16:00,640 --> 00:16:02,200
Come what may.
不管發生什麼

160
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:06,960
"All I need right now is a drink. Just let me have one more drink."
“我現在隻需要喝一杯，隻要再喝一杯”

161
00:16:08,080 --> 00:16:10,120
I can't stop myself.
我無法阻止自己

162
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:14,240
There this writer called Bukowski, you might've heard of him.
有一位作家叫佈科夫斯基，你可能聽說過他

163
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,520
You know what he said?
你知道他說什麼嗎？

164
00:16:17,280 --> 00:16:19,760
He said drinking is a form of suicide.
他說喝酒是自殺的一種形式

165
00:16:20,520 --> 00:16:26,040
He said drinking yourself unconscious is attempted suicide.
他說喝酒使自己昏迷那是企圖自殺

166
00:16:26,120 --> 00:16:29,800
- I don't want to die, Cemil. - Are you sure?
-我不想死，塞米爾  -你確定嗎？

167
00:16:29,880 --> 00:16:34,240
Of course I am. I don't even want to talk about this.
當然  我甚至一點都不想談論這個

168
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:37,640
